---
title: Sweet Chilli Glazed Chicken with Garlic-Ginger Rice & Veggie Stir-Fry
description: Every bite of this tasty meal is infused with flavour - from the steamed rice with garlic and ginger, to the zesty stir-fried veggies to baked chicken with a sweet chilli glaze. Dive in to a bowl of delicious delights!
image: https://img.hellofresh.com/f_auto,fl_lossy,h_640,q_auto,w_1200/hellofresh_s3/image/sweet-chilli-glazed-chicken-8d8954dc.jpg
